'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 38''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 38''',  was the 38th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''. There were two different covers for this issue, and it largely reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 58|''Star Wars Insider'' 58]]

